##Algorithms in Real Life

Let's take a look at how algorithms work in real life! 

**Make a copy of the [activity guide](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1zCe5nxpYzzU7C9rF-D9rqVfpgwgSzOcjShuh2UpeWuw/view) to get started:**

1. In Part 1, you will debug a music recommendation algorithm.

2. In Part 2, you will explore ethical considerations for a self-driving car algorithm.  The video link can be found [here](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1yxxJ_YiA2CiEt1V82Nl3HfcK7IoK9xol/view).

